description:
Add some combined artifacts.
Four spirit orbs → Five-element beads;
Warrior Token + Warrior Medal + Medal of Courage → Imperial Seal;
Lucky Bird + Lucky Clover + Prophecy Card → Dragon Ball;
Speed Cloak + Speed Necklace + Traveler's Ring → Phoenix Feather Ring;
Knight's Gloves + Swift Boots → Cloud-treading Boots;
Speed Cloak + Speed Necklace + Traveler's Ring + Knight's Gloves + Swift Boots → Phantom Gale Ring；
Add the treasure Golden Thunder Bamboo, and there is a chance to cast the Divine Thunder for Exorcising Evil when attacking.
